Installation Instructions
=========================

Prerquisites
------------

	- gcc
        - GNU make
        - perl (for Perl bindings)
        - debhelper (for building a debian package)


Procedure
---------

make
make install

All files will be installed below the top-level directory specifed in
the PREFIX file. Default is /usr/local, edit the file to change this.

The Makefile also supports the DESTDIR mechanism for relocating the
tree that's be installed at installation time.

make deb

can be used to build a Debian package.
